Wed, Jun 17, 2020, 7:42 PM
to me, Michael, Taylor, Nate, Jd

I'll let the cat out of the bag for our call tomm.
After a lengthy review of alternatives, we havedecided that we are going to use the VerifoneEngage line of terminals for our go forwardintegrated solution.

This will be released under the project name"Spartan", so please be discreet as nothing isformally released. We expect our go live date tobe 10/1.

We will not auto ship any of the integratedterminals to the installed base of merchants (Iknow that one will make Michael happy)

We could start writing to the P200/V400mintegrations right now, since we have an activeproject going on with them.

We should be able to have something ready in thelantic by the end of year.

We will have some time to answer questions tomm,but just wanted to give everyone the heads uponce the decision was made.

Thanks,
Steve
